 ---                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
  1. Health Check                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
  // Request                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
  GET http://localhost:8000/health                                                                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  // Response  200                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  { "status": "ok" }
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
  2. Get All Users

  // Request
  GET http://localhost:8000/users

  // Response  200                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  {
    "users": [                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
      { "id": 1, "name": "Alice" },                                                                                                                                                                                                        
      { "id": 2, "name": "Bob" }
    ]
  }

  ---
  3. Create User

  // Request
  POST http://localhost:8000/users
  { "name": "New User" }

  // Response  201
  { "id": 3, "name": "New User" }

  ---
  4. Get Single User

  // Request
  GET http://localhost:8000/users/1   (any id)

  // Response  200
  { "id": 1, "name": "Alice" }

  ---
  5. Replace User (Full Update)

  // Request
  PUT http://localhost:8000/users/1
  { "name": "Updated User" }

  // Response  200                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  { "id": 1, "name": "Updated User" }
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
  6. Update User (Partial Update)

  // Request
  PATCH http://localhost:8000/users/1
  { "name": "Patched User" }
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
  // Response  200
  { "id": 1, "name": "Patched User" }                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  ---
  7. Delete User

  // Request
  DELETE http://localhost:8000/users/1

  // Response  204
  (no body)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
  ---
  8. Slow Endpoint (1.5s delay)                                                                                                                                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  // Request
  GET http://localhost:8000/slow

  // Response  200  (after 1500ms)
  { "message": "This response was intentionally delayed" }
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
  ---
  9. Server Error                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  // Request
  GET http://localhost:8000/error

  // Response  500
  { "error": "Internal Server Error", "message": "Something went wrong" }
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
  ---
  10. Unauthorized                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  // Request
  GET http://localhost:8000/unauthorized

  // Response  401
  { "error": "Unauthorized", "message": "Missing or invalid token" }

  ---
  11. Custom Headers

  // Request
  GET http://localhost:8000/custom-headers

  // Response  200
  // Headers: X-Custom-Header: my-value, X-Request-Id: abc-123
  { "message": "Response includes custom headers" }
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
  ---
  These are the static mocks from the YAML. You can add more on the fly via POST /admin/mocks without restarting the server.                          